SKCM BRAF-V600 (secondary reference, n=206 samples):
  SOS1:    +3.231  DAMPER (strongest)
  EGFR:    -0.348  near-zero (V600 shifts EGFR toward neutral)
  BRAF:    +0.175  near-zero (structural BRAF self-reorganization)
  MAP2K1:  -0.645  near-zero

